# Bambu Studio

Use [Bambu Lab Wiki](https://wiki.bambulab.com/en/software/bambu-studio/studio-pages-outline) as the reference for:

- **Printer Settings**: Bambu printers, AMS, multi-device
- **Print Settings**: Slicing params, supports, seam, brim, variable layer height
- **Multi-Color**: Color painting, filament waste reduction, AMS usage
- **Calibration**: Flow rate, dynamic flow calibration

Project layout:
- `slicer/bambu-studio/printer/` — printer configs (P2S, A1, etc.)
- `slicer/bambu-studio/process/` — print presets
- `slicer/bambu-studio/filament/` — material profiles
